                        <interp inst="t18480612-name-195" type="surname" value="BRITTAIN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480612-name-195" type="given" value="CHARLOTTE"></interp>CHARLOTTE BRITTAIN</persName>
                  </hi>. I had this watch to take care of—I locked it up in my drawer—I saw it safe about ten minutes before twelve o'clock on the Wednesday—I went out, and left no one at home but the prisoner—I after<lb></lb>wards missed it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q</hi>. Why did Rodda give it to you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> It had an acci<lb></lb>dent—the prisoner lodged in the house, and two young men.</p>
